♪Drowned in sadness♪

749
00:44:30,280 --> 00:44:32,680
♪Just to see through♪

750
00:44:32,975 --> 00:44:35,025
♪I will whisper love to you♪

751
00:44:35,025 --> 00:44:37,225
♪For a lifetime♪

752
00:44:37,225 --> 00:44:41,440
♪End the worry in the world♪

