00:44:41,800 --> 00:44:42,960
♪It's worth it♪

754
00:44:42,960 --> 00:44:46,000
♪I'll be there for you all my life♪

755
00:44:46,175 --> 00:44:48,160
♪After the moments of beauty♪

756
00:44:48,160 --> 00:44:50,880
♪You are my reason to be♪

